long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Form templater is simple tool for fill forms on page quickly by custom templates. You can create templates for use in domains/pages. Templates can contains static and dynamic data. Dynamic data can be generated by using build in generators like IBAN number generator etc.
